            <a href="https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va8sOrp4SpkEQKVElV1i" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WhatsApp</a>
            <a href="https://t.me/DealsHubIndiaa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Telegram</a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/dealshubindia.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a>
